sentences: The band was formed in Klagenfurt in 1987.
A gig in Germany with Pungent Stench led to a deal with Nuclear Blast in 1989.
The band took a break in 1994 .
This timeout lasted until 2002 after their debut album Expositionsprophylaxe had been re-issued they released studio album, titled Ahead.
In October 2016 after a long break the band released their new album called Fear of Angst.
Disappeared with Hermaphrodite Choirs (compilation LP, 1990) on Witchhunt Records
